{"tid":279111,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過鍾意一個陌生人？？","createTime":"2017-06-11T04:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T04:37:06.000Z","uid":122322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f138130ce16cfda963a07326314f0353ade5a3d7","tid":279111,"uid":122322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:17:36.000Z","msg":"話說前晚同個fd去游水<br />\n本身我都好專心操水嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無啦啦我同個女仔係咁互望<br />\n痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n望親佢都見佢都係望緊我<br />\n就算我上水拉筋都係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n根據我嘅猜測<br />\n佢係同呀媽黎游嘅<br />\n跟住發現佢叫呀媽走先去沖涼先<br />\n一個人游<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我fd見我係咁望個女仔<br />\n就鼓勵我游過去池邊識下佢<br />\n但游到去我又驚青 唔敢開口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n冇幾耐個女仔走左<br />\n我個fd話佢回頭望我，但係我又唔敢望佢<br />\n果一刻勁後悔，拿拿聲上水沖涼換衫<br />\n諗住響出面等佢（我知我咁做好似好變態）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係等到泳池關門都唔見人<br />\n先知已經太遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我發現做左咁多年人，d毒撚性格都係改變唔到 <br />\n係一個定左型嘅毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我個fd話我其實有時你只係需要廿秒勇氣<br />\n但我連呢廿秒勇氣都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而件事已經過左兩晚，個心仍然係囉囉攣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都a1咗一段時間，差唔多兩年冇動過情<br />\n估唔到今次我竟然會鍾意左個陌生女仔<br />\n<br />\n你話我叫春又好，ff 都好，<br />\n做左咁耐CD-ROM 真係第一次開post<br />\n打出嚟只係想發洩下<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QU0oeghlCB4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQU0oeghlCB4&d=J%2FdDR1h%2FRUzdpwiA6Y8oy8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=dc60d460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QU0oeghlCB4</a><br />\n呢兩日係咁loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我決定左下個禮拜同一時間再去泳池<br />\n睇下撞唔撞到佢，撞唔到下個禮拜再繼續<br />\n我唔想再放棄每一個機會<br />\n想做就要做，就算失敗，起碼我做過，唔會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd62480289d4d01bb00d61aa0d5d4d4fe6203fb","tid":279111,"uid":23305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:32:29.000Z","msg":"毒撚最忌太有自信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f34d171e0fe9a43fde91b71ea93951791ac1a4f","tid":279111,"uid":81203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:37:06.000Z","msg":"勸你唔好自作多情"}]}